{
  "stem": "7832.4",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And we were already in the camp about a month, and we were already like, ready-- we were losing weight, but we-- we, I guess, looked still OK.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So they selected 15 of us for smooth skin.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And-- Did you remember the name of the doctor?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Did you ever hear it?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It could have been Eichmann.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It could have been Mengele.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know, after a while, they all look the same, and it didn't-- it wasn't important, you know, to us, what their names were.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They were our enemy and we need-- we needed to be strong when they came around.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We-- we pinched our cheeks, and we hit our neighbors so they'd look healthy.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So when they look at us, so they don't take us into that chimney.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And so I-- I, for one, wasn't interested in what their names were or where they came from.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "All I know is that they're not our friends.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we need to be very, very careful what we do and what we say to speed up the process of our death, if-- if we want to still live in this misery.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And most of the time we didn't, but we did anyway.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And so we were selected, 15 of us, for-- for smooth skin, and we didn't know what that meant.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And nobody would-- we would ask our-- the block [INAUDIBLE], which she was Polish, and we don't-- I-- to the very day, I don't know whether she was Jewish or she was not Jewish, but she was-- she was in there for a long time.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And if she was Jewish, then the reason she was mean is because she saw too much.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I forgive her for whatever she did.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
